Generic single-database configuration.

Commands should be run from the backend/recommender_api/ directory.

Create Migration Script
=======================

.. code-block:: bash

    cd backend/recommender_api
    alembic -c alembic_recommender.ini revision -m "create track vectors table"

Run Migration
=============

.. code-block:: bash

    cd backend/recommender_api
    alembic -c alembic_recommender.ini upgrade head